-- Canadian Real Estate Group Cuts Home Sales 2010 Forecast to 1.2 Percent
-- Greg Quinn
-- 2010-07-30T13:07:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/canadian-real-estate-group-cuts-home-sales-2010-forecast-to-1-2-percent.html

          
          
             The Canadian Real Estate Association
cut its home sales  forecast , it said in a statement released
from Ottawa today.  
 Sales will fall 1.2 percent this year to 459,600 units, the
report said.  
